This is Perl module EBook::EPUB::Valid.

INSTALLATION

EBook::EPUB::Valid installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % cpan EBook::EPUB::Valid

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

EBook::EPUB::Valid documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc EBook::EPUB::Valid

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

